cast.overview: When their latest scheme goes awry, Mayor Humdinger and his nephew Harold accidentally divert a meteor towards Adventure Bay. The meteor's golden energy grants the PAW Patrol superpowers. The heroic Mighty Pups are on a roll to super-save the day.
cast.title: PAW Patrol: Mighty Pups

details.biography: Samuel Faraci is an actor and singer, based in Los Angeles - CA, known for his work on Will & Grace (2018), An American Girl Story: Maryellen 1955 - Extraordinary Christmas (2016), Schooled (2019), Paw Patrol (2015), Rusty Rivets (2016), A Family Man (2016), Odd Squad (2015) and Wyrm (2019).
details.name: Samuel Faraci
